name: Rebirth as a Tiger: Sister is the Reborn Empress!
summary: After transmigrating, Jiang Che discovered that he had become a little Northeast Tiger in a zoo, together with a brother and sister.Jiang Che discovered that he could hear the inner thoughts of his brother and sister.His brother is actually the reincarnation of an Ancient Demon Monarch and the younger sister is the reincarnation of a future human Empress.Fortunately, Jiang Che activated the binding feedback system, where the strength of those bound to him strengthens him tenfold in return.
author: Uploading 30000 words dailyI become divine.
